      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — isothermal benchtop",
      "description": "Simulated velocity fields compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements at five flow-speed operating points. All experiments conducted at room temperature with isothermal blood analogue fluid. Mean absolute error in mid-plane velocity magnitude < 8% across all operating points. No thermally loaded test condition included."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/vr-02-hemolysis-index",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Normalised index of haemolysis (NIH) bench comparison — isothermal",
      "description": "Predicted normalised index of haemolysis compared against in-vitro bench measurements using porcine blood at 21 °C across five operating points. Predicted RH values within 12% of measured values at all points. Validation matrix covers isothermal conditions only; viscous-dissipation heating and bearing thermal load not represented in any test article or test condition."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/vr-03-pressure-head",
