      "name": "Pump pressure-head curve validation",
      "description": "CFD-predicted pressure rise versus flow rate compared against water-loop measurements across the full operating envelope. Agreement within 5% at all design-point flows. Provides hydraulic fidelity evidence but does not address thermal coupling to blood damage."
    }
  ],
